<STARTDOC>
macro(setauthorstring(name))
(Defines tt(name) as the `Author information' string, by default
em(AUTHOR INFORMATION). E.g., after tt(setauthorstring(AUTOR)),
YODL outputs this portuguese string to describe the author information.
Currently, it is relevant only for txt.)
<>

DEFINEMACRO(setauthorstring)(1)(\
    SETSYMBOL(XXauthorstring)(ARG1)\
)
